<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">凑整调零法(二)，是指乘数接近整十、整百......时，可先将被乘数凑为整十、整百.....倍再加上其零数倍数乘数的一种求积方法。可运用乘法对加法的分配率进行速算。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">19×102=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">19×102</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=19×(100+2)</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=19×100+19×2</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=1900+38</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=1938</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>